    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained, making it a solid choice for a reliable daily driver. The exterior paint still holds a deep shine, though a close inspection will reveal some minor stone chips on the hood and a few light surface scratches consistent with its age. Inside, the interior is clean and smoke-free, with only minor wear on the seat bolsters and steering wheel. Mechanically, the car is sound, having received regular oil changes and scheduled maintenance, ensuring it is ready for many more miles on the road.",
